Quant Flow
for Banks

Keep up with the pace of innovation with programmable accounts and financial products that enhance digital banking, optimise cash management and unlock new revenue streams.

Ready to unlock the potential of programmable money?

 

Book a meeting

New revenue streams.

Create new suites of intelligent money management products that seamlessly integrate with existing accounts and offer hyper-personalised experiences that drive engagement and loyalty. From predictive cash flow management to automated savings and lending solutions. Quant Flow enables you to accelerate innovation and rapidly bring new products into the market.

Monetised transactional fees.

Programmable money enables new pricing models based on execution logic, approval workflows and risk parameters for high-value payment. By charging fees on automated treasury movements and smart B2B payments, banks can generate long-term growth in non-interest income from high frequency, automated transactions.

Stay ahead
of the
competition.

Fintech startups and tech giants are expanding into banking, offering frictionless financial experiences. By adopting the same technology-driven approach, banks can reclaim their leading position and drive long-term growth.

Legacy systems can hinder digital transformation. Our modular, API-first platform enables seamless integration with existing infrastructure, allowing banks to effectively scale new solutions without costly system overhauls.
